messages.message: not the slightest clue @Jonathan Shih. could easily be stuff david / ted wrote that we wouldn’t know about any more as well. definitely check in with hari / balaram
I think I’m just going to go the route of adding another piece of information into the ibocr so we won’t affect any existing work

“I’m planning to make a change such that the metadata list of each record will contain only the pages contained within the record” <- sounds like though the data format is changing? would you change the interface code to make sure the same stuff is returned to client code? @Jonathan Shih
I think worst case, I will add a new field into IBDoc, so that the existing fields are not affected. I think there may be another way to be more backwards compatible too. I’m looking into this now
